Class MidiNoteGUIPopupMenu

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.MenuElement

    public class MidiNoteGUIPopupMenu
extends javax.swing.JPopupMenu
    A MidiNoteGUIPopupMenu represents the right-click menu for any MidiNoteGUI object. This also pops up as the right click on a NoteDisplayer.
    Since:
    1.0
